ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v23.group

Class PPP_PCB_ORDER

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v23.group.PPP_PCB_ORDER
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class PPP_PCB_ORDER
extends AbstractGroup

    Represents a PPP_PCB_ORDER group structure (a Group object). A Group is an ordered collection of message segments that can repeat together or be optionally in/excluded together. This Group contains the following elements:

    • 1: ORC (Common order segment)
    • 2: PPP_PCB_ORDER_DETAIL (a Group object) optional
